733357f-b.title: Thanksgiving ragamuffins, No.22-24.
733357f-b.text:
(1) Thanksgiving Ragamuffins, 1933, No. 22.  Another group picture in front of 383 Bleecker Street.  November 20, 1933.  P. L. Sperr.  NO REPRODUCTIONS

(2) No. 23.  On Bleecker Street, in front of the same real-estate office shown in No. 19.  November 30, 1933.  P. L. Sperr.  NO REPRODUCTIONS.

(3) No. 24.  A little gypsy in Greenwich Village; the location is uncertain.  November 20, 1933.  P. L. Sperr.  NO REPRODUCTIONS.
